  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mfrac><mroot><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>5</mn></msup><mn>4</mn></mroot><mroot><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mn>3</mn></mroot></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>/</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow></msup></math></p>\n<p>If the equation above holds for all positive values of <em>x</em>, what is the value of <math><mi>a</mi><mo>/</mo><mi>b</mi></math>?</p>",
